metadata.description:
Death came for me and I obliged  
I've been weary of this world of pain  
Death came for me and I rejoiced  
I welcomed the Necromancer with open arms  
Death came for me and I smiled  
Finally I'd be free, finally I'd be at peace,  
Death came for me and I held him by the hand
metadata.name: Death Came For Me #1/3
